This game was developed on the starter code provided for the Anagrams workshop. 
This workshop was part of the Applied CS with Android course: 
held in MESCOE,pune on 27-01-2018 by the Google facilitator Ms.Jyoti Chabaria

Presently the app is provide functionality 
to user to play in 3 modes
1.Simple Mode : Anagarams Of Same Length
2.Intermediate Mode :Anagarams with one extra letter
3.Hard Mode :Anagarams with two extra letters

Hoping to add following featues
1.Improve GUI
2.More Complexity
3.Updating Scoreboard(i.e Calculating Score and HighScore)

http://g.co/cswithandroid

Check the website for detailed instructions on how to implement this activity.

Version 1.0
